1.0.0.name: wordpress/sempress
1.0.0.description: SemPress is a highly semantic, HTML5 template, responsive and seo optimized. SemPress supports most of the new HTML5 tags, the new HTML5 input-types, microformats, microformats v2 and microdata (Schema.org).
